@Node "GMS_mailer_Call_Node" "GMS_mailer.guide/ARexx commands/GMS_mailer_Call_Node"
@Next "GMS_mailer_Call_Number"
@Prev "GMS_mailer_System_Version"
@Toc "ARexx Commands"

@{b}GMS_mailer_Call_Node@{ub}


Arguments: <mailer name>, <node>, [retries], [delay], [FORCE, ASYNC]

   Calls the system node.

   retries: Times the retries... or -1 for default.
   delay:   Set the RedialDelay... or -1 for default.

   FORCE:   Abort the current session.
   ASYNC:   Send directly the request and it doesn't queue in the arexx
            list.


@EndNode

