@Toc "ARexx Commands"

@{b}GMS_mailer_Call_Number@{ub}


Arguments: <mailer name>, <phone number>, [retries], [delay], [FORCE, ASYNC]

   Calls the system.

   retries: Times the retries... or -1 for default.
   delay:   Set the RedialDelay... or -1 for default.

   FORCE:   Abort the current session.
   ASYNC:   Send directly the request and it doesn't queue in the arexx
            list.


Results:   See <GMS_mailer_Status> results.

@EndNode

