@Node "GMS_CallNode.rexx" "GMS_mailer.guide/Scripts/GMS_CallNode.rexx"
@Next "GMS_CallNumber.rexx"
@Toc  "Scripts"

   @{b}GMS_CallNode.rexx@{ub}


Arguments: <line number> <retries> <delay> <nodes>

   Calls one or more nodes.


  o line number: the line of the mailer
  o retries:     set the number of retries (-1 for default)
  o delay:       set the redial delay. (-1 for default)
  o nodes:       nodes to call

Example:   rx GMS:Rexx/GMS_CallNode 1 -1 -1 2:331/213@fidonet.org

@EndNode

