@Prev "GMS_CallNode.rexx"
@Toc  "Scripts"

   @{b}GMS_CallNumber.rexx@{ub}


Arguments: <line number> <retries> <delay> <phone number>

   Calls the system.


  o line number:  the line of the mailer
  o retries:      set the number of retries (-1 for default)
  o delay:        set the redial delay. (-1 for default)
  o phone number: the phone numer of the system to call

Example:   rx GMS:Rexx/GMS_CallNode 1 -1 -1 2:331/213@fidonet.org

@EndNode

