   @{b}GMS_General.rexx@{ub}


Arguments: <command> <line number> [<argument> [',' <argument> ...]]

   Execute one ARexx command of GMS, for example:

      Rx General.gms GMS_mailer_Call_Node 0 , 2:331/106.0@fidonet.org


  o command:     the arexx command
  o line number: the line of the mailer
  o argument:    the argument of the command

