   @{b}GMS_TestSession.rexx@{ub}


Arguments: <line number> <log level> <log string>

   You can use this command to test your external commands.


  o line number: line of the mailer
  o log level:   the level of the LogUser
  o log string:  the string to write to the log

Example:   rx GMS:Rexx/GMS_TestSession 1 Silent "%o %i"

